	<br/>The 101st MIBN continues to defend in-depth along the international boundary. Our recon forces are to deploy south of the demilitarized zone in order to destroy enemy recon forces and prevent them from securing key terrain. A/101 is continuing to defend BP Alpha and the forward disruption zone. C/101 is defending BP Charlie.
	<br/>
	<br/><font color='#FFA500'>1.c.2.) Adjacent Units</font>
	<br/>A/101 MIBN (Radon Company) continues to defend North of the demilitarized zone along BP Alpha. B/101 MIBN (Ruda Company) continues to defend the town of Charkia.\
